{"tid":2308365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湖北推15頁微笑規範　不及格影響職評　網民：連點笑都要管","createTime":"2020-12-01T23:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T00:54:19.000Z","uid":271829,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c866e41814a02137fb8a77fd3c8168d91d6a8cec","tid":2308365,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T23:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nTsYNT3O00qZTWFBjVEOYjQIy28=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7HLSZN2S5RGODJGBJ2DKEOG3RQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnTsYNT3O00qZTWFBjVEOYjQIy28%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7HLSZN2S5RGODJGBJ2DKEOG3RQ.jpg&h=59c52eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江蘇西湖風景區的導遊在2017年時，也須接受咬筷子、頂手機的微笑訓練。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bnMjR_GoMH4S-tsksz5gm49w6a4=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F7L7PFBLZVD4DMKHJBZYRIDAK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbnMjR_GoMH4S-tsksz5gm49w6a4%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF7L7PFBLZVD4DMKHJBZYRIDAK4.jpg&h=1607e0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地不同地方的政府部門也要求受訓，提供微笑服務。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n湖北省市場監督管理局日前發佈15頁《規範》，湖北省文化和旅遊廳周二起正式實施首個「微笑服務」地方標準，要求各景區工作人員，無論表情、言行、儀態及語氣，甚至手部角度也要符合《規範》要求。<br />\n《規範》對觀光區員工各種儀態標準仔細分類，例如，目光部份便分有3點，要求員工正視遊客「眼睛或T部位」，以示尊重友善；目光要和善真誠；及神情專注平視遊客。<br />\n至於微笑時，面部表情要自然放鬆，嘴角微微上翹，以及親切真誠地微露牙齒。<br />\n甚至手的「角度」也有規範，「向遊客指示方向時，手指自然併攏，掌心側向上45&deg;。指示近處目標時，手臂與身體夾角呈120&deg;-150&deg;；指示遠處目標時手臂伸直；眼睛需兼顧遊客和指示目標，面帶微笑。」面對遊客查詢，回答用字也有一套文明用語的標準答案。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201202/Z2OL7K6TLJF2RFDXM27RSYWN3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201202%2FZ2OL7K6TLJF2RFDXM27RSYWN3U%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2f2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=bf53738c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201202%2FZ2OL7K6TLJF2RFDXM27RSYWN3U%2F&h=6c8d006d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201202/Z2OL7K6TLJF2RFDXM27RSYWN3U/</a>"},{"pid":"362a67bf6fe08d6632e21185cfb72cd5ee1ef15f","tid":2308365,"uid":155095,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T23:32:09.000Z","msg":"去廁所都要管埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2810000/2810341/34444_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2810000%2F2810341%2F34444_1024.jpg&h=7186abb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"654f55247a000ee49c855c81204e092a0046881b","tid":2308365,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T23:32:58.000Z","msg":"支共真係病態式控制欲"},{"pid":"00d36ef035ad604e081e52f046d3eebf8a40348e","tid":2308365,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T23:36:40.000Z","msg":"中國人是要管的"},{"pid":"598a981ad17bca25ab59315b6e6cc9ec5ca605a1","tid":2308365,"uid":259120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T23:38:23.000Z","msg":"西朝鮮化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec8790df6869e6a460301b45a12fa0f78cb3b33","tid":2308365,"uid":32691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T23:41:58.000Z","msg":"湖北雞賣慣笑<br />\n<br />\n小意思啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa268e92cfaf205f50edb1c396edfc44392ddcab","tid":2308365,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T23:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />強迫"},{"pid":"8710348ff9ba4b79c5175d1a